OL,4,G2100FHighway Thru Hell
OL,5,     GHeavy snow has created avalanche
OL,6,     Gconditions and closed the Coq in
OL,7,     Gboth directions. With trucks
OL,8,     Gusing back roads, Jamie's team is
OL,9,     Gcalled out to recover a semi
OL,10,     Gthat's gone over a cliff.
OL,11,G2200FMotorway: Hell on the Highway
OL,12,     GThe consequences of driving in
OL,13,     Gextreme weather, from a tornado
OL,14,     Gwreaking havoc on a camper van in
OL,15,     GArkansas, to a battle royale in
OL,16,     GVirginia between a flash flood
OL,17,     Gand a hybrid car.
OL,18,G2300FThe X-Files
OL,19,     GA supernatural killer whom Mulder
OL,20,     Ghelped to imprison is released on
OL,21,     Gparole, and a deadly game of cat-
OL,22,     Gand-mouse begins.
